dct_title_s: Venezuela 1:1 400 000 / World Mapping Project, we just map it powered by the Map Alliance. (Western)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, gradient tints, and spot heights. Depths shown by gradient tints. Road map with tourist features. Title from panel. At head of title on panel: Reise Know-How. "© Copyright 2002 by Map Alliance International ..." Includes index and location map. "World mapping project." "One world - one series."
dct_publisher_sm: Bielefeld [Germany] : Reise Know-How Verlag Peter Rump GmbH, 2002.
